parameters.description: Maximum phytoplankton growth rate (aggregated to model time step)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Upper bound on phytoplankton specific growth, modulated by nutrient and temperature

parameters.description: Half-saturation constant for phytoplankton nutrient uptake
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Monod half-saturation for nutrient limitation of phytoplankton growth

parameters.description: Maximum zooplankton grazing rate on phytoplankton
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Upper bound on zooplankton ingestion rate per biomass, before saturation/shape effects

parameters.description: Half-saturation constant for zooplankton grazing response
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Controls saturation of grazing at low phytoplankton concentrations

parameters.description: Grazing response shape exponent (1=Type II; >1=Type III-like)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Exponent controlling low-P suppression and nonlinearity in grazing functional response

parameters.description: Zooplankton assimilation efficiency of grazed phytoplankton
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Fraction of ingested phytoplankton converted to zooplankton biomass (remainder egested to dissolved/particulate pool)

parameters.description: Phytoplankton mortality/exudation rate to dissolved/particulate pool
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Non-grazing loss rate of phytoplankton (exudation, viral lysis, sinking)

parameters.description: Zooplankton mortality rate with remineralization fraction r_min to dissolved nutrient
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Background mortality of zooplankton; a fraction remineralizes to nutrient pool

parameters.description: Fraction of plankton mortality/release that remineralizes to dissolved nutrient each time step
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Controls how much mortality/exudation is returned to dissolved nutrient versus other loss pools

parameters.description: External nutrient input to the mixed layer (e.g., vertical mixing/upwelling)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Net external supply of dissolved nutrient per time step

parameters.description: Optimal sea surface temperature for phytoplankton growth response
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Temperature at which phytoplankton maximum growth is achieved in the Gaussian modifier

parameters.description: Curvature of Gaussian temperature effect on phytoplankton growth (larger = narrower optimum)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Controls sensitivity of phytoplankton growth to SST deviations from T_opt

parameters.description: Observation/process error SD for nutrient (lognormal)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Standard deviation of lognormal error for nutrient concentration

parameters.description: Observation/process error SD for phytoplankton (lognormal)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Standard deviation of lognormal error for phytoplankton concentration

parameters.description: Observation/process error SD for zooplankton (lognormal)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Standard deviation of lognormal error for zooplankton concentration

parameters.description: Initial dissolved nutrient concentration (parameterized; no data initialization)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Initial NPZ state for nutrient; used when NPZ observation data are absent

parameters.description: Initial phytoplankton concentration (parameterized; no data initialization)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Initial NPZ state for phytoplankton; used when NPZ observation data are absent

parameters.description: Initial zooplankton concentration (parameterized; no data initialization)
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Initial NPZ state for zooplankton; used when NPZ observation data are absent
